Class Request

java.lang.Object
entities.Request
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChangeTitleRequest, DeregisterRequest, ProjectRequest, TransferStudentRequest
public class Request extends Object
The Request class represents a request made by a user for some action to be taken. The requestorID field represents the user who made the request. The status field represents the current status of the request. The requestID field is a unique identifier assigned to each request.
